{"tid":1796783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實罷工真係有咁難？驚無咗份工，快啲入工會","createTime":"2019-12-25T00:45:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T09:45:19.000Z","uid":13355,"like":63,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"7ed862049c61a8aa5bb5536a83dda03946088af4","tid":1796783,"uid":13355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T00:45:27.000Z","msg":"黑鼠日日殺人，你仲掛住返工，驚無咗份工，其實唔好意思難聽啲講句，你都好冷血，香港警鼠日日殺人癲到咁，你扮無嘢，之後日子仲難過，衰過60年代。<br />\n入工會，罷工啦。<br />\n利申，入左"},{"pid":"93c786490480ca087305f2f5115ce74e15341b1f","tid":1796783,"uid":145292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T00:48:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b6fde4f9ad080a2dcb7b2cb6069a5343c0aa540","tid":1796783,"uid":62259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T00:50:27.000Z","msg":"裝睡的港豬叫不醒"},{"pid":"af25c21aebd366584651cbc7376d43824e9cad5b","tid":1796783,"uid":260036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T00:52:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d23e8c0c4cae42ada371773b868fcf446b837de","tid":1796783,"uid":216776,"like":4,"dislike":9,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T00:54:12.000Z","msg":"因為你無實質證據罷工可以爭取更加好的生活，都無證據表明會變返60年代咁差，係現實吖，無係你個人信就有用"},{"pid":"80ef065a2eaed91851764a33d2f1bc50ef146bfc","tid":1796783,"uid":13355,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T01:30:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為你無實質證據罷工可以爭取更加好的生活，都無證據表明會變返60年代咁差，係現實吖，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無</span></span>係你個人信就有用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n拼音？"},{"pid":"694a64e66f853f850f48af8134e753cc790bdb3e","tid":1796783,"uid":13355,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"2d23e